{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "AI models have also been developed to classify AMD severity and predict disease progression.",
    "Grassmann et al.",
    "trained a CNN to classify AMD severity into four levels based on OCT images, achieving an accuracy of 92.1%, with a quadratic weighted kappa of 0.90, indicating substantial agreement with human graders (19).",
    "developed a CNN model that could predict the risk of AMD progression over two years with an AUC of 0.92, suggesting that AI could potentially guide personalized management and follow-up strategies for AMD patients (20).",
    "The integration of AI into clinical workflows for AMD management has also been explored."
  ],
